Ayo.

1106
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:48,000
Ayo, Zheng Dedong.

1107
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:50,190
Ayo, ayunan.

1108
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:51,870
Ayo.

1109
00:42:51,870 --> 00:42:54,150
Cepat.

1110
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:56,710
Sebenarnya aku sudah sedikit menduganya.

1111
00:42:56,710 --> 00:42:57,560
Karena aku berpikir,

1112
