1113
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:03,710
Itu sepertinya mustahil.

1114
00:43:03,710 --> 00:43:05,470
Rasanya agak aneh.

1115
00:43:05,470 --> 00:43:06,710
Akhirnya tidak disangka,

1116
00:43:06,710 --> 00:43:09,560
