untukku dan Zheng Dedong.

1117
00:43:09,560 --> 00:43:10,600
Aku sungguh terkejut.

1118
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:11,870
Apa?

1119
00:43:11,870 --> 00:43:14,760
Kalian bilang apa padaku?
Katanya, Fu Jie mau naik ayunan?

1120
00:43:14,760 --> 00:43:16,470
Menurutku, Fu Jie...

1121
00:43:16,470 --> 00:43:17,870
Fu Jie naik ayunan.

1122
00:43:17,870 --> 00:43:19,390
Tampak kasar tapi sebenarnya halus, mengerti?

1123
00:43:23,320 --> 00:43:25,560
Guo Xu juga merencanakannya dengan teliti.

1124
00:43:25,560 --> 00:43:27,670
Menurutku, dia sangat perhatian.

1125
00:43:27,670 --> 00:43:29,760
Saat dia bilang kepadaku

1126
00:43:29,760 --> 00:43:31,840
