1129
00:43:36,040 --> 00:43:36,390
Benar.

1130
00:43:36,390 --> 00:43:38,430
Sekarang, mari kita persilakan...

1131
00:43:38,430 --> 00:43:40,230
Terima kasih.

1132
00:43:40,230 --> 00:43:40,950
Biar kupegangkan bolanya.

1133
00:43:40,950 --> 00:43:41,950
Terima kasih.

1134
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:44,760
Terima kasih.

1135
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:46,190
Ayo.

1136
00:43:46,340 --> 00:43:49,900
