1178
00:45:33,710 --> 00:45:35,910
Mereka sungguh sudah bekerja keras.

1179
00:45:35,910 --> 00:45:38,320
Benar, mereka sangat tulus.

1180
00:45:38,320 --> 00:45:39,520
